  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help ELIL Extend its Support to Refugees on Samos</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">After three years of successful work on Lesvos, ELIL is extending its operations to the Greek island of Samos. Vathy camp hosts almost 7,000 asylum seekers, ten times its official capacity. No state-provided support is available to them ahead of their all-important asylum interview. Your contribution can help our staff and volunteers uphold the rule of law, defend human rights and ensure meaningful access to legal aid on the island. Donations are tax deductible in the UK, US and Germany.</narrative>
  </description>
